  "detailed_description": "<h1>联系我们</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531950/extras/e240cc12e8fe0d10eb8b14926993b579.avif?t=1732262628\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531950/extras_big/e240cc12e8fe0d10eb8b14926993b579.avif?t=1732262628 width=800 height=108 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A massacre that wiped out a village that has been left in the dust for more than ten years, a shuttle between reality and dreams. As Chen Xi returns to the ruined village, the truth of two seemingly unrelated cases is revealed...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, players are forced to fall between reality and dreams;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The puzzles incorporate a large number of traditional Chinese folklore elements, such as: Five Elements, Bagua, Yin and Yang, etc...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect known clues and understand the plot and entries to affect scene changes by dragging, combining, and rotating text entries;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve every puzzle in the game and uncover the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531950/extras/0096710086ef3dfda6443629c4386fd1.poster.avif?t=1732262628\" width=616 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531950/extras/0096710086ef3dfda6443629c4386fd1.webm?t=1732262628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531950/extras/0096710086ef3dfda6443629c4386fd1.mp4?t=1732262628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531950/extras/e240cc12e8fe0d10eb8b14926993b579.avif?t=1732262628\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531950/extras_big/e240cc12e8fe0d10eb8b14926993b579.avif?t=1732262628 width=800 height=108 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A massacre that wiped out a village that has been left in the dust for more than ten years, a shuttle between reality and dreams. As Chen Xi returns to the ruined village, the truth of two seemingly unrelated cases is revealed...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, players are forced to fall between reality and dreams;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The puzzles incorporate a large number of traditional Chinese folklore elements, such as: Five Elements, Bagua, Yin and Yang, etc...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect known clues and understand the plot and entries to affect scene changes by dragging, combining, and rotating text entries;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve every puzzle in the game and uncover the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531950/extras/0096710086ef3dfda6443629c4386fd1.poster.avif?t=1732262628\" width=616 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531950/extras/0096710086ef3dfda6443629c4386fd1.webm?t=1732262628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531950/extras/0096710086ef3dfda6443629c4386fd1.mp4?t=1732262628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
